	<td><span class="topic">Are test ROMs cheating?</span><br /><span class="gensmall"><a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=10726">http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=10726</a></span></td>
