		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Correct. Test ROMs don't make bugs magically disappear, rather they point out where your code is going wrong and that is what I don't like.<br /><br />Of course having the ability to port a homebrew test ROMs to actual hardware negates everything and IMHO is the best option.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
